00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:29.960
<i>♪ Especially when I see you</i>
<i>I keep seeing the scenes ♪</i>

00:00:30.040 --> 00:00:33.400
<i>♪ From when we were together ♪</i>

00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:36.600
<i>♪ But I keep seeing you in my head ♪</i>

00:00:36.840 --> 00:00:41.320
<i>♪ My broken heart hasn't recovered ♪</i>

00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:43.920
<i>♪ So I hurt you ♪</i>

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:49.240
<i>♪ Even though I have to</i>
<i>Make myself watch you cry ♪</i>

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:55.520
<i>♪ I hate it but I still do it ♪</i>
\N
\N

00:00:55.520 --> 00:00:59.480
<i>♪ I keep picking at scabs to hurt you ♪</i>
\N
\N

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:07.000
<i>♪ I want to escape</i>
<i>But it feels like walking in circles ♪</i>

00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:11.760
<i>♪ In the end I hurt myself</i>
<i>Keeping my love hidden ♪</i>

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:15.000
<i>♪ I can't walk away even if I want to ♪</i>

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:20.000
\N
\N
<i>♪ My love must be hidden</i>
<i>I can hardly stand it ♪</i>

00:01:20.040 --> 00:01:22.920
<i>♪ It's torture when you cry ♪</i>
\N
\N
\N

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:26.800
<i>♪ The more you're hurt ♪</i>

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:30.880
<i>♪ The weaker my heart becomes ♪</i>

00:01:31.520 --> 00:01:37.360
<i>♪ I try not to love you</i>
<i>Holding back my tears while saying goodbye ♪</i>

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:41.600
<i>♪ But I could never do it for real ♪</i>

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:45.320
Are you serious, or just joking?

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:47.600
<i>Do you think I have time</i>
<i>to joke around with you?</i>

00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:49.560
<i>What? Lada said</i>
<i>she wouldn’t go back to her?</i>

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:51.400
She said she had moved on.

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:53.000
She’s moving on in a circle.

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:55.160
Don't be too nice to me.

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:56.320
Why not?

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:57.320
I might fall even more for you.

00:01:57.360 --> 00:01:58.560
<i>It hasn’t even been long,</i>

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:00.120
and she’s already so infatuated
that she doesn’t come home.

00:02:00.160 --> 00:02:02.200
I don’t believe that it’s true happiness.

00:02:02.240 --> 00:02:04.720
Loving the same sex is not a flaw.

00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:06.960
We have something more interesting.

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:09.800
Dr. Wisanu and Dr. Fahlada

00:02:09.880 --> 00:02:11.200
are getting married.

00:02:23.920 --> 00:02:26.000
What did you agree on with my mother?

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:29.120
I really didn’t know that

00:02:29.160 --> 00:02:30.960
Auntie would say something like that.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:32.480
You didn’t know?

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:34.240
If you didn’t know,

00:02:34.360 --> 00:02:36.520
why did you go along with my mother?

00:02:39.880 --> 00:02:40.880
Well...

00:02:41.920 --> 00:02:43.560
Because I want to marry you.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:46.800
When did we ever love each other?

00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:50.240
When did I ever love you romantically?

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:54.520
I know.

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:55.640
I can wait.

00:02:56.880 --> 00:02:58.000
Nu,

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:00.120
I already have someone I love.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:02.680
Don’t waste your time on me.

00:03:03.640 --> 00:03:05.760
But the elders want us to get married.

00:03:06.960 --> 00:03:08.720
I think we can’t avoid it.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:11.680
You’re willing to get married

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:13.480
just to obey the elders

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:15.800
even though we don’t love each other?

00:03:15.800 --> 00:03:17.160
If it’s the elders' wish,

00:03:18.720 --> 00:03:19.760
I don’t mind.

00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:23.960
But I do.

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:41.560
Why are you doing this, Mother?

00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:46.320
I'm not an object that you can do
whatever you want with.

00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:48.000
I have feelings too.

00:03:49.040 --> 00:03:50.280
But I am your mother.

00:03:51.240 --> 00:03:53.680
I have the right to choose
what’s best for my child.

00:03:54.200 --> 00:03:55.120
No,

00:03:55.960 --> 00:03:57.160
not in this case.

00:03:57.640 --> 00:03:58.760
I won’t agree to it.

00:03:58.880 --> 00:04:00.320
You behaving this way

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:02.240
is exactly why I have to do this.

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:04.400
Even though you know

00:04:04.440 --> 00:04:06.160
I don’t want to marry Nu,

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:08.720
even though you know I don’t like Nu.

00:04:09.400 --> 00:04:10.920
And the person you want to marry,

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:12.200
can you marry them?

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:24.000
Mother,

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:26.480
I'm begging you.

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:30.400
Just this matter, don’t force me.

00:04:31.640 --> 00:04:32.640
No.

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:34.600
You have to marry Nu only

00:04:35.200 --> 00:04:36.680
because Nu is the most suitable

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:38.080
and appropriate person for you.

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:40.800
What does suitability mean, Mother?

00:04:40.840 --> 00:04:43.080
Whatever I deem suitable is suitable!

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:45.880
You have no right to question it.

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:14.160
YOU HAVE THREE MESSAGES

00:05:15.080 --> 00:05:15.960
CONGRATULATIONS!

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:17.400
WHEN IS THE WEDDING?

00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:19.680
DON’T FORGET TO GIVE ME AN INVITATION CARD!

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:24.000
I’M ALREADY GETTING MY DRESS READY

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:24.760
WOW!

00:05:24.760 --> 00:05:29.840
CONGRATULATIONS TO YOU!

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:57.120
EXTREMELY WARM MARRIAGE ANNOUNCEMENT

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:59.520
BETWEEN TWO HEIRS FROM TWO FAMOUS FAMILIES

00:05:59.520 --> 00:06:03.880
DR. WISANU AND DR. FAHLADA

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:14.600
Doctor…

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:16.680
Earn,

00:06:18.640 --> 00:06:20.080
you saw the news, right?

00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:23.920
Have a seat.

00:06:31.080 --> 00:06:32.320
Earn,

00:06:32.600 --> 00:06:33.600
You see...

00:06:33.600 --> 00:06:36.080
I didn’t expect my mother
to give an interview like that.

00:06:37.880 --> 00:06:39.600
Do you understand?

00:06:40.160 --> 00:06:41.160
I tried,

00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:43.080
-I…
-Hey.

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:48.560
Are you tired?

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:02.080
Tired.

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:07.240
Very tired.

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:35.080
I’m here for you.

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:45.560
Thank you.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:09.000
Thank you.

00:08:21.840 --> 00:08:22.840
Come here.

00:08:37.760 --> 00:08:39.679
Please take off your shoes, Doctor.

00:08:43.480 --> 00:08:45.800
Move your legs a little, come on.

00:08:57.320 --> 00:08:58.320
Comfortable.

00:09:12.280 --> 00:09:14.080
Don’t get tired of my problems.

00:09:24.360 --> 00:09:27.440
I will never get tired of your problems.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.000
Promise?

00:09:34.760 --> 00:09:35.760
I promise.

00:12:14.480 --> 00:12:15.960
Are you here to see Lada?

00:12:16.600 --> 00:12:17.600
Yes.

00:12:18.080 --> 00:12:19.080
Umm...

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:22.000
Lada might be busy with a case right now.

00:12:23.280 --> 00:12:24.240
That's okay,

00:12:24.560 --> 00:12:25.520
I can wait.

00:12:25.680 --> 00:12:26.680
Thank you.

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:28.480
Umm...

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:30.360
I think it might be

00:12:31.040 --> 00:12:32.560
a waste of time for you.

00:12:33.120 --> 00:12:35.200
Maybe you should schedule
a meeting another day.

00:12:36.640 --> 00:12:37.680
It’s fine.

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:38.960
Since I’m already here,

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:41.040
I’ll wait in the doctors’ lounge.

00:12:41.800 --> 00:12:42.800
Okay.

00:12:48.720 --> 00:12:50.680
A good person with no place to belong.

00:12:55.440 --> 00:12:57.120
These flowers are an apology.

00:13:07.480 --> 00:13:08.960
If you're truly sorry,

00:13:09.320 --> 00:13:10.680
then don't do it again.

00:13:11.880 --> 00:13:13.240
It might seem selfish,

00:13:13.400 --> 00:13:14.960
but I really like you, Lada.

00:13:15.240 --> 00:13:16.280
Like me...

00:13:16.960 --> 00:13:19.320
Even though you know you're hurting me?

00:13:27.960 --> 00:13:30.320
You know I can't go against my mother,

00:13:31.400 --> 00:13:32.600
but you still do this.

00:13:35.160 --> 00:13:36.800
Even if I had no one else,

00:13:36.880 --> 00:13:38.400
we couldn't love each other.

00:13:46.320 --> 00:13:48.720
Because I really can't love someone like you.

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:54.000
Lada.

00:14:16.600 --> 00:14:18.920
Don’t you think you were too harsh?

00:14:18.920 --> 00:14:21.000
Dr. Wisanu isn’t that bad.

00:14:23.240 --> 00:14:24.680
How is he not bad?

00:14:25.560 --> 00:14:26.960
He knows I don’t like him,

00:14:26.960 --> 00:14:28.560
yet he still wants to marry me?

00:14:29.840 --> 00:14:32.240
Maybe he thinks that

00:14:32.720 --> 00:14:35.320
if you stay together,
you’ll eventually love him.

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:38.080
That’s never going to happen.

00:14:39.760 --> 00:14:40.760
Lada,

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:42.440
let me ask you something.

00:14:42.840 --> 00:14:44.760
Are you never going to love a man?

00:14:44.880 --> 00:14:45.960
That’s right.

00:14:46.600 --> 00:14:47.680
I love women,

00:14:48.400 --> 00:14:50.720
and that woman has to be Earn only.

00:14:54.480 --> 00:14:55.840
Are you sure

00:14:56.200 --> 00:14:58.200
you’re ready for the pressure

00:14:58.240 --> 00:15:00.320
that’s going to hit you out of nowhere?

00:15:02.080 --> 00:15:03.080
I’m ready.

00:15:07.240 --> 00:15:08.200
Then

00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:10.920
you’d better hold on to Earn's hand tightly.

00:15:34.120 --> 00:15:35.240
Get well soon.

00:15:40.440 --> 00:15:41.400
Professor.

00:15:54.600 --> 00:15:56.360
I must apologize on Lada’s behalf.

00:15:56.920 --> 00:15:59.200
She’s been under a lot of stress lately

00:15:59.240 --> 00:16:00.840
and might be a bit short-tempered.

00:16:02.960 --> 00:16:04.600
I think I’m the cause.

00:16:11.680 --> 00:16:13.680
You’ve been quite persistent lately,

00:16:14.360 --> 00:16:16.000
always trying to win her over.

00:16:16.560 --> 00:16:18.720
Do you want to marry Lada that much?

00:16:20.640 --> 00:16:21.720
Well,

00:16:21.920 --> 00:16:23.200
both our families

00:16:23.240 --> 00:16:24.480
want us to get married.

00:16:26.840 --> 00:16:28.800
So just because your families want it,

00:16:29.360 --> 00:16:31.000
you have to go through with it?

00:16:32.360 --> 00:16:33.200
Yes,

00:16:33.560 --> 00:16:34.880
our marriage would

00:16:35.520 --> 00:16:37.240
benefit both our family businesses.

00:16:38.960 --> 00:16:40.560
Do you love Lada?

00:16:45.520 --> 00:16:46.560
Honestly,

00:16:48.600 --> 00:16:50.280
I’m starting to doubt it myself.

00:16:52.520 --> 00:16:54.360
You know so much about business,

00:16:55.000 --> 00:16:57.000
but do you understand your own heart?

00:17:00.200 --> 00:17:01.240
My  heart?

00:17:03.560 --> 00:17:04.599
My own heart?

00:17:04.800 --> 00:17:05.880
Yes.

00:17:07.359 --> 00:17:10.000
Have you ever truly listened to your heart?

00:17:10.880 --> 00:17:12.640
Maybe it’s telling you

00:17:13.800 --> 00:17:15.400
something different.

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:36.720
So, did you get a chance

00:17:36.760 --> 00:17:38.440
to talk about the wedding with Lada?

00:17:40.400 --> 00:17:41.560
Not yet.

00:17:43.160 --> 00:17:45.880
It's hard enough to talk about the weather.

00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:48.240
Nu.

00:17:53.520 --> 00:17:54.640
Auntie,

00:17:55.520 --> 00:17:57.760
I think Lada already has someone she likes.

00:18:00.400 --> 00:18:01.080
I...

00:18:01.080 --> 00:18:02.080
Nu.

00:18:03.200 --> 00:18:04.880
You can't give up now.

00:18:05.920 --> 00:18:09.560
I've already announced to the media
that you and Lada are getting married.

00:18:09.600 --> 00:18:12.120
And there's our
families' businesses to consider.

00:18:12.360 --> 00:18:14.080
You must marry Lada,

00:18:14.640 --> 00:18:16.280
or everything will fall apart.

00:18:23.360 --> 00:18:24.360
Yes, Auntie.

00:18:33.200 --> 00:18:34.000
<i>Tomorrow?</i>

00:18:34.120 --> 00:18:35.040
Yes.

00:18:35.400 --> 00:18:36.800
There's a hospital management

00:18:36.800 --> 00:18:38.400
training session in Pattaya tomorrow.

00:18:38.440 --> 00:18:39.640
I want you to attend.

00:18:40.000 --> 00:18:41.000
Why me?

00:18:41.960 --> 00:18:44.760
Because you’ll be managing
our hospital in the future.

00:18:45.440 --> 00:18:46.880
It has to be you.

00:18:49.320 --> 00:18:50.680
Am I going alone?

00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:55.400
Nu will be going too.

00:19:01.720 --> 00:19:02.960
So,

00:19:03.240 --> 00:19:05.200
do you want me to attend the training,

00:19:06.400 --> 00:19:08.880
or do you just want me
to go to Pattaya with Nu?

00:19:17.840 --> 00:19:20.120
Work is more important than personal matters.

00:19:25.440 --> 00:19:26.800
Just do as I say.

00:19:33.920 --> 00:19:34.880
Yes,

00:19:34.920 --> 00:19:36.480
Lada left early this morning.

00:19:36.640 --> 00:19:38.360
She should be arriving soon.

00:19:38.880 --> 00:19:40.080
Thank you very much.

00:19:40.240 --> 00:19:42.800
<i>I've arranged for Lada's room</i>
<i>to be next to yours.</i>

00:19:42.960 --> 00:19:45.360
You need to make an effort and impress her.

00:19:45.680 --> 00:19:47.200
I have high hopes for this trip.

00:19:47.880 --> 00:19:48.920
Yes,

00:19:49.320 --> 00:19:51.240
I'll make the most of this opportunity.

00:19:54.200 --> 00:19:55.200
Goodbye.

00:20:09.800 --> 00:20:11.080
Hello, Professor.

00:20:12.560 --> 00:20:13.560
Hello.

00:20:13.920 --> 00:20:16.560
What brings you here?

00:20:17.360 --> 00:20:18.600
And...

00:20:21.160 --> 00:20:22.280
where is Lada?

00:20:28.400 --> 00:20:29.440
Wait,

00:20:30.240 --> 00:20:31.360
what did you say?

00:20:32.200 --> 00:20:34.600
You want me to attend
the training in your place?

00:20:34.600 --> 00:20:35.480
Yes.

00:20:35.480 --> 00:20:36.360
In Pattaya?

00:20:36.360 --> 00:20:37.360
Uh-huh.

00:20:37.440 --> 00:20:38.760
With Dr. Wisanu?

00:20:39.040 --> 00:20:39.840
Yes.

00:20:39.840 --> 00:20:41.160
Are you crazy, Lada?

00:20:41.200 --> 00:20:42.880
Your mom will kill me!

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:47.320
If you're not going,
you don't get to drink this.

00:20:50.080 --> 00:20:51.360
Tan,

00:20:51.880 --> 00:20:53.520
a friend in need is a friend indeed.

00:20:54.720 --> 00:20:57.080
Yeah. If a friend doesn’t help a friend,

00:20:57.080 --> 00:20:58.320
they're a dog.

00:20:58.400 --> 00:20:59.720
So, are you going or not?

00:20:59.840 --> 00:21:02.160
Otherwise, I'll start preparing
dog food for you.

00:21:02.200 --> 00:21:03.440
How about liver flavor?

00:21:03.800 --> 00:21:05.560
Oww!

00:21:06.080 --> 00:21:07.280
Please help me.

00:21:08.920 --> 00:21:10.080
Liver flavor then.

00:21:11.760 --> 00:21:12.600
Hmm?

00:21:12.640 --> 00:21:14.000
Help or not?

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:15.400
I'm not going!

00:21:18.680 --> 00:21:20.320
Even though I'm here but

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:22.600
you only asked for Lada,

00:21:25.160 --> 00:21:26.400
I also feel a bit hurt.

00:21:32.120 --> 00:21:34.400
Fahlada had a prior commitment today,

00:21:34.760 --> 00:21:37.280
so she couldn't make it.
I'm here as her replacement.

00:21:38.320 --> 00:21:39.320
Oh,

00:21:40.240 --> 00:21:41.240
I see.

00:21:46.200 --> 00:21:48.720
This case is critical.
Please handle it with care.

00:21:49.920 --> 00:21:50.920
Yes.

00:21:51.160 --> 00:21:52.160
Lada.

00:21:54.240 --> 00:21:54.920
Mother.

00:21:54.920 --> 00:21:56.760
Didn't you go to the training today?

00:21:57.320 --> 00:21:59.480
I had an urgent case

00:21:59.520 --> 00:22:01.520
I had to attend to since this morning.

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:04.160
Then who is responsible for the training?

00:22:04.240 --> 00:22:05.720
I asked Tan to go.

00:22:06.480 --> 00:22:07.320
What?

00:22:07.360 --> 00:22:10.120
Tan has taken management classes
with me before.

00:22:10.440 --> 00:22:11.800
You can trust him.

00:22:12.400 --> 00:22:13.320
Also,

00:22:13.840 --> 00:22:15.200
this case is crucial.

00:22:15.600 --> 00:22:17.920
Didn't you say once that

00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:19.800
work is more important

00:22:19.840 --> 00:22:21.240
than personal matters?

00:22:32.080 --> 00:22:33.840
So, you sent Tan instead?

00:22:34.160 --> 00:22:35.160
Yeah.

00:22:37.400 --> 00:22:38.680
That's really cheeky.

00:22:38.720 --> 00:22:40.400
Wasn't your mother furious?

00:22:40.720 --> 00:22:41.640
I don't know.

00:22:41.720 --> 00:22:43.160
I just acted casually.

00:22:43.440 --> 00:22:45.280
She probably couldn't say anything.

00:22:49.880 --> 00:22:50.760
Doctor.

00:22:50.800 --> 00:22:51.800
Hmm?

00:22:52.960 --> 00:22:55.400
What if one day you found out
your mother did something

00:22:55.400 --> 00:22:57.640
behind your back without
telling you again?

00:22:57.680 --> 00:22:58.840
Would you be angry?

00:23:00.240 --> 00:23:01.280
I don't know.

00:23:02.040 --> 00:23:03.240
Why do you ask?

00:23:04.520 --> 00:23:05.880
I'm just asking randomly.

00:23:09.120 --> 00:23:10.080
Then

00:23:10.120 --> 00:23:12.480
let's stop talking about others.

00:23:13.680 --> 00:23:14.720
I'm hungry.

00:23:15.040 --> 00:23:16.440
Let's go eat something.

00:23:16.840 --> 00:23:18.200
Good idea.

00:23:18.240 --> 00:23:20.200
I'll cook something for you.

00:23:24.360 --> 00:23:25.440
What is it?

00:23:25.520 --> 00:23:27.000
You said you were hungry.

00:23:27.000 --> 00:23:28.760
I'm going to cook for you.

00:23:30.040 --> 00:23:31.520
When I said I was hungry,

00:23:32.000 --> 00:23:33.440
I meant I'm hungry for you.

00:23:34.200 --> 00:23:36.040
I want to eat you more.

00:23:43.280 --> 00:23:44.760
Where did you get that from?

00:23:46.640 --> 00:23:47.640
Didn't work, huh?

00:23:50.040 --> 00:23:51.040
Oh...

00:23:54.000 --> 00:23:55.240
It didn't work?

00:23:55.800 --> 00:23:59.360
Tan said it would definitely work.

00:23:59.520 --> 00:24:01.200
If you had a partner, then...

00:24:03.680 --> 00:24:05.400
Shouldn't have listened to Tan.

00:24:07.400 --> 00:24:08.400
Then

00:24:08.680 --> 00:24:11.640
I'll go make some food for you.

00:24:14.560 --> 00:24:15.800
It was weird, darling.

00:24:23.400 --> 00:24:24.800
Geez,  Tan.

00:24:25.880 --> 00:24:27.160
Shouldn't have listened to him.

00:24:28.840 --> 00:24:30.840
You know so much about business,

00:24:31.320 --> 00:24:33.240
but do you understand your own heart?

00:24:33.600 --> 00:24:36.200
Have you ever truly listened to your heart?

00:24:36.280 --> 00:24:37.960
Maybe it’s telling you

00:24:39.080 --> 00:24:40.680
something different.

00:24:54.600 --> 00:24:56.040
What's with the mood?

00:24:56.080 --> 00:24:57.400
Drinking alone like this?

00:25:02.120 --> 00:25:03.920
Just thinking about what you said.

00:25:06.040 --> 00:25:07.320
My words

00:25:08.240 --> 00:25:10.040
really stuck with you, huh?

00:25:33.200 --> 00:25:35.880
I never really thought about my own heart before.

00:25:38.160 --> 00:25:39.200
All this time,

00:25:40.640 --> 00:25:42.120
I've probably been a robot.

00:25:44.680 --> 00:25:46.160
And what did you figure out?

00:25:50.200 --> 00:25:51.360
I don't know.

00:25:51.360 --> 00:25:53.400
For now, it's just a hypothesis.

00:25:54.760 --> 00:25:56.600
As for the answer from my heart,

00:25:57.040 --> 00:25:58.240
it'll take time

00:25:59.840 --> 00:26:01.280
and a way to prove it.

00:26:02.880 --> 00:26:04.200
Sounds complicated.

00:26:08.000 --> 00:26:09.200
Or...

00:26:11.480 --> 00:26:13.320
