00:26:15.760 --> 00:26:16.880
How?

00:26:59.320 --> 00:27:02.120
I want to be with you like this every day.

00:27:03.200 --> 00:27:04.440
Before bed,

00:27:04.440 --> 00:27:06.920
I want to see you as the last person,

00:27:09.920 --> 00:27:12.920
and when I wake up,
I want you to be the first person I see.

00:27:12.920 --> 00:27:14.400
Would that be good?

00:27:15.000 --> 00:27:17.240
That means I'd be tired every day.

00:27:22.040 --> 00:27:23.120
How about

00:27:25.000 --> 00:27:27.000
