00:27:40.480 --> 00:27:42.360
I want to take you on a gondola ride

00:27:43.280 --> 00:27:44.640
in Venice.

00:27:45.880 --> 00:27:46.600
Uh-huh.

00:27:46.640 --> 00:27:49.040
We'll ride a boat together.

00:27:49.880 --> 00:27:52.320
We'll float away,

00:27:52.800 --> 00:27:54.120
float away.

00:27:57.280 --> 00:27:58.600
Float away...

00:28:00.120 --> 00:28:02.160
No way!

00:28:03.840 --> 00:28:05.840
Help me, Doctor!

00:29:06.880 --> 00:29:09.000
How can you sit there working so calmly?

00:29:10.240 --> 00:29:12.240
And why shouldn’t I be able to work?

00:29:12.240 --> 00:29:14.280
Our daughter is back with that girl again.

00:29:14.280 --> 00:29:15.600
Well, that’s the right thing.

00:29:15.640 --> 00:29:16.880
How is that right?

00:29:19.840 --> 00:29:21.120
Actually,

00:29:21.240 --> 00:29:23.440
