00:29:26.440 --> 00:29:27.800
and made them break up.

00:29:29.000 --> 00:29:30.000
You knew?

00:29:30.080 --> 00:29:31.840
Of course, I knew everything.

00:29:32.600 --> 00:29:33.920
You went and instigated,

00:29:34.360 --> 00:29:35.680
threatening that girl

00:29:36.200 --> 00:29:37.800
to break up with our daughter,

00:29:38.840 --> 00:29:40.520
and you incited our daughter

00:29:40.840 --> 00:29:42.640
into misunderstanding everything

00:29:42.640 --> 00:29:44.160
without caring how much

00:29:44.200 --> 00:29:45.720
