00:29:45.800 --> 00:29:47.320
But I did it for her good.

00:29:48.280 --> 00:29:49.880
You did it for your own selfish reasons.

00:29:49.880 --> 00:29:51.640
I’ve kept quiet all this time

00:29:51.960 --> 00:29:53.280
because I knew talking

00:29:53.320 --> 00:29:55.000
wouldn’t change anything with you.

00:29:55.040 --> 00:29:56.160
People like you

00:29:56.200 --> 00:29:59.160
only realize the truth when it’s too late.

00:30:16.560 --> 00:30:18.120
<i>You went and instigated,</i>

00:30:18.760 --> 00:30:20.120
<i>threatening that girl</i>

00:30:21.040 --> 00:30:22.600
<i>to break up with our daughter,</i>

00:30:22.880 --> 00:30:24.560
<i>and you incited our daughter</i>

00:30:25.400 --> 00:30:27.160
<i>into misunderstanding everything.</i>

00:30:28.160 --> 00:30:31.840
<i>I have a patient with a brain tumor.</i>

00:30:32.600 --> 00:30:33.840
<i>Who is it?</i>

00:30:34.640 --> 00:30:35.960
She is

00:30:36.720 --> 00:30:38.480
the mother of a junior here.

00:30:39.080 --> 00:30:40.480
Is she that important

00:30:41.120 --> 00:30:43.400
that you had to call me for help?

00:30:43.920 --> 00:30:45.040
<i>I have someone else.</i>

00:30:45.080 --> 00:30:46.560
<i>I want to break up with you.</i>

00:30:48.040 --> 00:30:49.320
I don’t like women!

00:30:49.400 --> 00:30:51.080
I like men!

00:30:51.680 --> 00:30:53.000
I like men!

00:30:53.560 --> 00:30:54.560
Understand?

00:30:56.960 --> 00:30:57.960
Earn!

00:30:58.160 --> 00:30:59.920
Earn! Don't go!

00:31:00.400 --> 00:31:01.560
Earn!

00:31:02.960 --> 00:31:04.800
Earn!

00:31:05.320 --> 00:31:06.520
Earn!

00:31:14.240 --> 00:31:16.240
No...

00:31:19.840 --> 00:31:20.880
Earn is here.

00:31:22.400 --> 00:31:23.440
Earn is here.

00:31:23.560 --> 00:31:24.680
-Lada.
-Earn.

00:31:25.480 --> 00:31:26.680
Earn.

00:31:27.160 --> 00:31:28.160
Lada.

00:31:30.160 --> 00:31:31.160
Mother.

00:31:32.480 --> 00:31:33.760
Are you drinking, dear?

00:31:35.600 --> 00:31:36.600
Mother.

00:31:37.000 --> 00:31:38.680
Why are you so drunk?

00:31:45.080 --> 00:31:46.600
Mother.

00:31:50.800 --> 00:31:53.280
I can’t take it anymore!

00:31:59.120 --> 00:32:00.080
My dear.

00:32:00.880 --> 00:32:02.160
-Mother.
-Lada.

00:32:02.960 --> 00:32:04.320
Mother.

00:32:05.200 --> 00:32:08.080
I can’t take it anymore!

00:32:10.200 --> 00:32:12.480
Mother.

00:32:14.160 --> 00:32:15.760
When I visited her mother,

00:32:20.040 --> 00:32:21.840
I saw her with another man.

00:32:23.800 --> 00:32:25.880
They seemed very close,

00:32:29.040 --> 00:32:30.800
probably her new boyfriend.

00:32:39.160 --> 00:32:40.840
She probably just used us

00:32:41.520 --> 00:32:42.920
to get her mother treated.

00:32:44.760 --> 00:32:47.360
Once her mother was cured and safe,

00:32:48.440 --> 00:32:49.880
you became useless to her,

00:32:52.520 --> 00:32:53.840
so she left you.

00:32:58.840 --> 00:33:00.200
Mother.

00:33:00.840 --> 00:33:03.400
How could she leave me?

00:33:07.680 --> 00:33:09.120
You still have me.

00:33:11.600 --> 00:33:13.800
It doesn’t matter if no one else loves you.

00:33:17.240 --> 00:33:18.720
My love is enough.

00:33:22.840 --> 00:33:23.840
Mother.

00:33:32.840 --> 00:33:36.720
<i>♪ I have a heart and know how to love ♪</i>

00:33:37.480 --> 00:33:41.680
<i>♪ Especially when I see you</i>
<i>I keep seeing the scenes ♪</i>

00:33:41.960 --> 00:33:44.680
<i>♪ From when we were together ♪</i>

00:33:45.480 --> 00:33:47.880
<i>♪ But I keep seeing you in my head ♪</i>

00:33:48.880 --> 00:33:52.480
<i>♪ My broken heart hasn't recovered ♪</i>

00:33:53.440 --> 00:33:55.680
<i>♪ So I hurt you ♪</i>

00:33:55.920 --> 00:34:01.040
<i>♪ Even though I have to</i>
<i>Make myself watch you cry ♪</i>

00:34:06.560 --> 00:34:07.720
Has Lada come back?

00:34:07.760 --> 00:34:09.560
Yes, she’s been back for a while.

00:34:09.639 --> 00:34:11.120
She came in without saying a word

00:34:11.159 --> 00:34:12.800
and went straight to her room.

00:34:21.360 --> 00:34:23.040
Lada, what are you doing?

00:34:23.719 --> 00:34:25.120
I'm moving in with Earn.

00:34:27.600 --> 00:34:28.960
Why are you moving out?

00:34:32.639 --> 00:34:34.600
I visited Father this morning.

00:34:35.600 --> 00:34:37.120
I heard everything.

00:34:43.080 --> 00:34:45.719
You were the one who made
me and Earn break up,

00:34:46.719 --> 00:34:49.600
even though you saw how heartbroken I was.

00:34:49.840 --> 00:34:53.239
How could you let me live
with that pain for years?

00:34:53.960 --> 00:34:55.120
Is this

00:34:55.760 --> 00:34:57.800
