00:35:07.160 --> 00:35:08.160
Lada.

00:35:11.240 --> 00:35:12.240
Lada.

00:35:18.400 --> 00:35:19.400
Lada.

00:35:20.720 --> 00:35:21.720
Lada.

00:35:22.520 --> 00:35:23.880
Listen to me.

00:35:25.240 --> 00:35:26.640
It’s not like that.

00:35:26.680 --> 00:35:28.200
Not like that? Then what is it?

00:35:30.480 --> 00:35:33.240
I did it because I love you
and wanted the best for you.

00:35:34.800 --> 00:35:36.080
Wanted the best for me?

00:35:39.640 --> 00:35:41.040
You mean causing me pain and

00:35:41.080 --> 00:35:42.720
heartbreak was for my good?

00:35:44.720 --> 00:35:46.560
That’s not love or good intentions.

00:35:51.360 --> 00:35:52.840
But the path you're choosing

00:35:54.040 --> 00:35:55.040
is wrong.

00:35:58.800 --> 00:35:59.840
Really?

00:36:02.480 --> 00:36:05.040
All this time, I did everything you wanted.

00:36:05.200 --> 00:36:07.240
I did everything you thought was right.

00:36:09.880 --> 00:36:11.560
You wanted me to become a doctor,

00:36:11.560 --> 00:36:12.560
so I did.

00:36:12.680 --> 00:36:14.920
You wanted me to do anything, I obeyed.

00:36:17.120 --> 00:36:18.360
But do you know?

00:36:19.120 --> 00:36:20.760
I was never happy.

00:36:23.640 --> 00:36:25.080
Not a single day.

00:36:29.720 --> 00:36:33.080
From now on,
I will choose what you think is wrong.

00:36:35.720 --> 00:36:37.400
I will choose to love Earn,

00:36:38.760 --> 00:36:42.440
and Earn will be
the last most important person in my life.

00:37:09.760 --> 00:37:10.920
Where are you going?

00:37:11.640 --> 00:37:12.640
Lada.

00:38:06.360 --> 00:38:07.360
Doctor.

00:38:09.480 --> 00:38:10.680
What happened?

00:38:13.560 --> 00:38:15.440
I know the whole truth now.

00:38:33.280 --> 00:38:36.800
My mother knew how much pain I was in,

00:38:40.480 --> 00:38:43.000
yet she still chose to hurt my feelings

00:38:45.560 --> 00:38:46.880
and Earn's.

00:38:53.280 --> 00:38:55.520
I don't understand why she did it.

00:39:10.840 --> 00:39:11.960
I'm sorry.

00:39:14.840 --> 00:39:15.880
I'm so sorry.

00:39:19.360 --> 00:39:20.480
I'm sorry.

00:39:23.680 --> 00:39:24.680
It's fine.

00:39:26.760 --> 00:39:28.040
I'm so sorry.

00:39:31.440 --> 00:39:32.480
Now I understand

00:39:33.680 --> 00:39:36.360
how much you must have suffered.

00:39:36.560 --> 00:39:37.640
I'm so sorry.

00:39:42.800 --> 00:39:43.960
I'm so sorry.

00:39:44.160 --> 00:39:45.360
It's all my fault,

00:39:45.760 --> 00:39:46.800
all my fault.

00:39:47.000 --> 00:39:48.040
Doctor,

00:39:48.240 --> 00:39:49.480
listen to me.

00:39:51.920 --> 00:39:53.640
Don't blame yourself.

00:39:54.880 --> 00:39:57.040
I never blamed you.

00:40:01.040 --> 00:40:02.600
Just being with you

00:40:03.680 --> 00:40:06.600
makes me happy.

00:40:08.800 --> 00:40:10.400
I'm truly happy, the happiest.

00:40:14.000 --> 00:40:15.480
The happiest.

00:40:17.160 --> 00:40:18.040
From now on,

00:40:18.080 --> 00:40:20.560
I won’t let anyone hurt our love again.

00:40:25.120 --> 00:40:26.480
But Doctor,

00:40:26.560 --> 00:40:27.600
listen to me,

00:40:28.440 --> 00:40:31.320
are you sure about this decision?

00:40:35.400 --> 00:40:38.240
This time, I'm following my heart.

00:40:48.840 --> 00:40:49.840
Then...

00:40:53.080 --> 00:40:55.080
What about your work at the hospital?

00:40:56.480 --> 00:40:57.600
What will you do?

00:41:53.240 --> 00:41:55.200
Wow, the lighting is perfect.

00:41:57.840 --> 00:41:59.800
Ratee, did you hear?

00:41:59.840 --> 00:42:02.520
Dr. Fahlada has resigned from the hospital.

00:42:02.560 --> 00:42:03.600
What?

00:42:03.600 --> 00:42:04.720
How do you know?

00:42:04.760 --> 00:42:06.080
Where did you hear that?

00:42:06.200 --> 00:42:08.080
She resigned from her own hospital?

00:42:08.120 --> 00:42:09.800
I just called to book

00:42:09.800 --> 00:42:11.640
a facial course at the hospital,

00:42:11.680 --> 00:42:12.480
