00:42:12.520 --> 00:42:14.400
Dr. Fahlada has resigned.

00:42:15.240 --> 00:42:16.560
Why would she resign?

00:42:16.600 --> 00:42:18.600
Wasn't there a marriage announcement?

00:42:18.880 --> 00:42:20.080
I don't know.

00:42:20.440 --> 00:42:21.720
Or is it because of love?

00:42:22.760 --> 00:42:25.200
She doesn't want to get married,
so she resigned?

00:42:26.400 --> 00:42:27.400
I can't believe someone

00:42:27.440 --> 00:42:29.800
like Dr. Fahlada would do anything

00:42:29.800 --> 00:42:31.160
for love.

00:42:31.200 --> 00:42:32.520
Doing anything for Earn.

00:42:33.760 --> 00:42:35.200
Who would do that?

00:42:38.160 --> 00:42:39.160
Hmm...

00:42:39.800 --> 00:42:42.440
Then you're heartbroken, aren't you?

00:42:45.400 --> 00:42:46.480
Yes,

00:42:46.520 --> 00:42:47.720
I'm heartbroken.

00:42:48.600 --> 00:42:50.560
Heartbroken even before I fell in love.

00:42:51.240 --> 00:42:52.880
They love each other so much,

00:42:53.080 --> 00:42:54.240
no one can compete.

00:43:11.320 --> 00:43:12.760
I can't believe

00:43:13.920 --> 00:43:15.600
this is our last supper.

00:43:16.720 --> 00:43:18.240
Our last meal together.

00:43:20.960 --> 00:43:23.600
We won't have moments
like this anymore, will we?

00:43:27.880 --> 00:43:29.400
Stop being so dramatic.

00:43:32.440 --> 00:43:33.880
I'm not dying.

00:43:34.680 --> 00:43:36.240
If you want to have meal,

00:43:36.920 --> 00:43:38.960
