00:43:40.520 --> 00:43:41.520
Well...

00:43:41.600 --> 00:43:43.200
It's just hard not to feel sad.

00:43:47.680 --> 00:43:49.000
Are you sure about this?

00:43:51.320 --> 00:43:53.160
You can still change your mind.

00:43:53.520 --> 00:43:54.520
Yeah.

00:43:56.640 --> 00:43:57.640
No.

00:43:58.480 --> 00:43:59.720
I've made up my mind.

00:44:02.560 --> 00:44:03.760
It's not just resigning,

00:44:05.080 --> 00:44:06.360
I'm cutting all ties with

00:44:06.360 --> 00:44:08.520
everything related to this hospital.

00:44:09.360 --> 00:44:11.240
So, you're leaving with just your body?

00:44:12.880 --> 00:44:13.880
Yes.

00:44:15.920 --> 00:44:17.600
I want to start anew

00:44:18.680 --> 00:44:19.880
on my own,

00:44:21.120 --> 00:44:22.920
relying on my abilities.

00:44:26.000 --> 00:44:27.920
Why are you going to such lengths?

00:44:29.080 --> 00:44:31.680
You're giving up everything.

00:44:33.960 --> 00:44:36.760
I just can't work with Mother anymore.

00:44:46.760 --> 00:44:48.800
If you need anything, just let me know.

00:44:50.320 --> 00:44:51.320
Alright?

00:44:53.840 --> 00:44:55.040
