00:45:25.480 --> 00:45:27.000
Please don't cry, Ms. Ros.

00:45:41.080 --> 00:45:42.760
<i>I will pass the medical exams</i>

00:45:43.440 --> 00:45:45.680
and help you and Father with the work,

00:45:46.480 --> 00:45:48.440
so you both won't have to be so tired.

00:45:52.080 --> 00:45:53.640
Do you think you're tiny?

00:46:12.280 --> 00:46:13.280
Don't be sad.

00:46:14.720 --> 00:46:16.200
Our child's life is their own.

00:46:18.120 --> 00:46:19.600
We're not their owners.

00:46:21.280 --> 00:46:23.240
Let them walk their path.

00:46:24.280 --> 00:46:25.400
But I can't accept it.

00:46:28.840 --> 00:46:29.960
I can't handle it.

00:46:33.440 --> 00:46:34.840
Lada is the seed

00:46:35.760 --> 00:46:37.520
I cultivated since birth.

00:46:43.760 --> 00:46:46.160
I sent her to learn being a doctor from you,

00:46:47.400 --> 00:46:48.760
to have a good conscience,

00:46:49.640 --> 00:46:52.880
to be a doctor who tries to save lives

00:46:55.640 --> 00:46:58.640
even if there's only a 1% chance.

00:47:09.600 --> 00:47:12.040
I groomed Lada to be a good director,

00:47:15.560 --> 00:47:17.560
an exceptional leader above the others.

00:47:20.800 --> 00:47:22.040
But everything's ruined

00:47:23.600 --> 00:47:24.640
because of that girl.

00:47:27.640 --> 00:47:29.640
How can two women love each other?

00:47:31.880 --> 00:47:32.880
Hmm?

00:47:34.720 --> 00:47:37.000
How can two women truly love each other?

00:47:37.600 --> 00:47:39.560
They can't build a proper family.

00:47:40.640 --> 00:47:42.280
It's impossible and you know it.

00:47:42.960 --> 00:47:44.080
I know you're hurt,

00:47:46.880 --> 00:47:49.160
but Lada is probably just as hurt as you.

00:47:54.800 --> 00:47:56.400
I want to talk to my daughter.

00:48:01.320 --> 00:48:03.120
I've never hit her.

00:48:05.400 --> 00:48:07.000
But I did.

